=====Usage notes=====
* {{term|thou|Thou}} is used with the archaic second-person singular of verbs, which usually ends in {{term|-est|lang=en}}, as in, for example, “Lovest '''thou''' me?” Irregular forms include: {{term|art#Verb|art}} (of {{term|be|lang=en}}), {{term|hast#Verb|hast}} (of {{term|have|lang=en}}), {{term|shalt|lang=en}} (of {{term|shall|lang=en}}), {{term|wost|lang=en}} (of {{term|wit#Verb|wit}}), and {{term|wilt|lang=en}} (of {{term|will#Verb|will}}).

